Focuser Server INDI driver
=================================
This package provides the INDI driver for a focuser server so other devices can remotely
control an INDI focuser without having to be an INDI client.

Requirements
============
* INDI
* CFITSIO
* LIBDC1394


Installation
============
See INSTALL


How to Use
==========
Once installed, the Focuser Server INDI driver can be used by a remote client such as
the iOS app specifically made to use this driver.

